{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}There is now an Allied Chat function, to share battle strategies with your teammates. This can be achieved either by the \b /colour\b0  command function or by pressing the appropriate F-key (which will always be F9 unless there are two people playing on the same machine but in different allied groups).\par
