{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}Allied chat colour mismatch fixed (this was a bug in the new Allied Chat feature of 3.5 Beta 1).\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}Utility selection key fixed for UK-layout keyboards. It is now the grave accent key (to the left of the \b 1\b0  key) in both layouts.\par
