\b\fs24 Features\b0\fs20\par
\pard{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf8\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\nowidctlpar\fi-180\li180 The French translations have been improved and corrected by JaBBa.\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}There is now a Map Extraction feature which can be applied on game recordings. Right-click on a \b .WAgame\b0  file and choose "\b Extract Map\b0 ", and the map will be saved in your \b User\\SavedLevels\b0  folder using the base name of the recording; you can then rename it to what you want.\par
