\b\fs24 Changes\b0\fs20\par
\pard{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf8\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\nowidctlpar\fi-180\li180 Recording is now a bit more streamlined: nothing is recorded while there is no controlling team (i.e. between turns)\cf1  [Note: Chat is still recorded between turns, but since there is currently no timing information, a chat that happened between turns will play back at the beginning of the next turn.]\cf0\par
