\b\fs24 Features\b0\fs20\par
\pard{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf8\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\nowidctlpar\fi-180\li180 In an offline game or playback, the ESC dialog box no longer closes automatically after minimising. This way, the game it will remain paused upon restoring until you press ESC again.\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}Added the ability to load colour maps that were saved in .CUS format using Beta 1/2/3pre1.\par
