\pard{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf8\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\nowidctlpar\fi-180\li180\b0\fs12 [DC, CS]\fs20  Some extra information is now logged into "palette.log".\par
